### Posts API Examples

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@contentType = application/json
@studentToken = your-student-jwt-token-here
@viewerToken = your-viewer-jwt-token-here
@postId = your-post-id-here

### Get all posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts

### Create post (multipart form-data for file upload)
# Use Postman or similar tool for file uploads
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/create
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

# Form data:
# mediaFile: [select file]
# caption: "Great training session today! ðŸ’ªâš½"

### Like a post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/like
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerToken}}

### Unlike a post  
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/like
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerToken}}

### Comment on a post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/comments
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerToken}}

{
  "content": "Amazing skills! Keep up the great work! ðŸ”¥"
}

### Get comments for a post
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/comments

### Get all comments for a post
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/comments?limit=all

### Save a post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/save
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerToken}}

### Unsave a post
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/save
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerToken}}

### Get user's saved posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/user-id-here/saved-posts
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerToken}}